# 1. Purpose

This document defines the long-term strategic direction of ATHENA.

Unlike the Manifesto, which defines our beliefs, this document defines our destination.

Every major product decision should support this vision.

---

# 2. Our Vision

> **To become the world's most trusted evidence-based Decision Intelligence Platform for financial markets, empowering investors with transparent, explainable and continuously improving AI-assisted decision support.**

ATHENA is designed to help users think better—not trade more.

---

# 3. Why ATHENA Matters

Markets are becoming increasingly complex.

Information is abundant.

Attention is limited.

Retail investors often have access to the same information as institutions but lack structured processes to transform that information into high-quality decisions.

ATHENA exists to close that gap.

---

# 4. The Future We Want to Build

We envision a platform where:

- Every investment decision is evidence-based.
- Every recommendation is transparent.
- Every risk is quantified.
- Every trade becomes research.
- Every mistake becomes knowledge.
- Every user continuously improves.

The platform should become more valuable with every decision made.

